<hw>Point`-de*vise"</hw>  }</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>at point devis</ets>; <ets>at</ets> at + <ets>point</ets> point, condition + <ets>devis</ets> exact, careful, OF. <ets>devis</ets> fixed, set. See <er>Device</er>.]</ety> <def>Uncommonly nice and exact; precise; particular.</def>⟦br⟧
